{
  "id": "percentage",
  "slug": "percentage-calculator",
  "name": "Percentage Calculator",
  "category": "math",
  "description": "Calculate percentages of numbers, find what percent X is of Y, and more.",
  "icon": "%",
  "tags": ["percentage", "percent", "ratio", "math"],
  "fields": [
    {
      "id": "percentage",
      "label": "Percentage (%)",
      "type": "number",
      "defaultValue": 20,
      "placeholder": "e.g. 20",
      "suffix": "%",
      "helpText": "The percentage value",
      "constraint": { "min": 0, "step": 0.1, "required": true }
    },
    {
      "id": "number",
      "label": "Of Number",
      "type": "number",
      "defaultValue": 150,
      "placeholder": "e.g. 150",
      "helpText": "The base number",
      "constraint": { "required": true }
    },
    {
      "id": "result",
      "label": "Result",
      "type": "computed",
      "precision": 4,
      "helpText": "Percentage of the number"
    },
    {
      "id": "remainder",
      "label": "Remainder (100% - x%)",
      "type": "computed",
      "precision": 4,
      "helpText": "What is left after removing the percentage"
    }
  ],
  "groups": [
    { "id": "inputs",  "label": "What is X% of Y?", "fields": ["percentage", "number"] },
    { "id": "outputs", "label": "Results",           "fields": ["result", "remainder"] }
  ],
  "formulas": {
    "result":    "(percentage / 100) * number",
    "remainder": "number - (percentage / 100) * number"
  },
  "explanation": "## Percentage Basics\n\nA percentage is a ratio expressed as a fraction of 100. The word comes from Latin *per centum*, meaning \"by the hundred.\"\n\n### Three core problems:\n\n1. **What is P% of X?** → Result = (P/100) × X\n2. **X is what % of Y?** → Percent = (X/Y) × 100\n3. **P% of what is X?** → Total = X / (P/100)",
  "examples": [
    { "label": "20% of 150",  "inputs": { "percentage": 20,  "number": 150  } },
    { "label": "15% tip on $60", "inputs": { "percentage": 15, "number": 60 } },
    { "label": "7.5% sales tax on $200", "inputs": { "percentage": 7.5, "number": 200 } }
  ],
  "chart": {
    "xAxisField": "percentage",
    "yAxisField": "result",
    "xRange": [0, 100],
    "points": 50,
    "label": "Result vs Percentage (base = current number)"
  }
}
